            "detailed_description": "<strong>Local multi-player game (2 to 4 players). Only playable with joystick/gamepads.</strong><br><br>Welcome to the world of Bomb N' Bats. What is this game ?  Well, to be simple, it's Bomberman meet Combat (Atari 2600) meet Unreal Tournament meet Pac-Man. No need to read a manual here : one stick to manage your bat and one button to launch a bomb. And to win a round, you must be the last bat alive. Let the rumble begin !!!<br><br> ---<br><br><i>Content of the Game:</i><br><br>- 2 to 4 players can play in the Deathmatch mode.<br><br>- All types of gamepads allowed (PS4, Xbox One, etc ...)<br><br>- 30 different levels, with some which will modify seriously the way of playing.<br><br>- Different bonus to boost your bat (or annoy the others).<br><br>- A new game mode : Team DeathMatch. You can play different combinations : 2 versus 2, 2 versus 1 or even 3 versus 1 if you feel strong enough.<br><br>- A Parameters menu where you can customize your experience.<br><br><br><br><br>Good game, and of course you can leave your comments below (it would be very much appreciated to help me improve the game and eradicate the bugs).",
